---
title: Harissa Roasted Pumpkin with Leafy Couscous & Herby Mayo
description: Couscous is a lovely way to finish the day, but what if there was a bit of green? Add some baby leaves to pop against the vibrant orange of the roast pumpkin. Finally, crumble little clouds of feta on top for the perfect way to tie this dinner together.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
